item.title: StackSample: 10% of Stack Overflow Q&A
item.description: Stackoverflow follows a ‘Question and Answer’ format and there are strict standards on the manner in which users can interact on the forum. Stackoverflow forum is used for many purposes including: Getting solutions to programming problems; Gaining generic information on programming languages and; Learning new concepts in programming. Dataset : https://www.kaggle.com/stackoverflow/stacksample In this project I tried to build a semantic search engine in which returns top 10 similar questions and top 10 relevant answers for the query or question asked by user within some milliseconds.
